WEBVTT

00:11.212 --> 00:15.582
♪ You're not alone,
together we stand ♪

00:15.584 --> 00:20.303
♪ I'll be by your side,
you know I'll take your hand ♪

00:20.305 --> 00:24.307
♪ and when it gets cold
and it feels like the end ♪

00:24.309 --> 00:30.797
♪ there's no place to go,
you know I won't give in ♪

00:30.799 --> 00:35.385
♪ No, I won't give in

00:36.954 --> 00:42.725
♪ Keep holding on

00:42.727 --> 00:45.962
♪ 'cause you know we'll make it
through, make it through ♪

00:45.964 --> 00:51.651
♪ Just stay strong

00:51.653 --> 00:55.304
♪ 'cause you know I'm here
for you, I'm here for you ♪

00:55.306 --> 00:57.490
♪ nothing you can say

00:57.492 --> 00:59.325
♪ nothing you can do

00:59.327 --> 01:03.813
♪ There's no other way
when it comes to the truth ♪

01:03.815 --> 01:09.752
♪ so keep holding on

01:09.754 --> 01:11.754
♪ 'cause you know
we'll make it through ♪

01:11.756 --> 01:13.706
♪ we'll make it through

01:13.708 --> 01:17.844
♪ So far away,
I wish you were here ♪

01:17.846 --> 01:22.682
♪ before it's too late,
this could all disappear ♪

01:22.684 --> 01:24.333
♪ before the doors close

01:24.335 --> 01:25.268
Thanks.

01:25.270 --> 01:27.137
♪ And it comes to an end

01:27.139 --> 01:33.509
♪ with you by my side
I will fight and defend ♪

01:33.511 --> 01:37.313
♪ I'll fight and defend

01:37.315 --> 01:39.515
♪ Yeah, yeah

01:39.517 --> 01:45.205
♪ Keep holding on

01:45.207 --> 01:49.025
♪ 'cause you know we'll make it
through, make it through... ♪

01:50.128 --> 01:52.912
Aah!

01:52.914 --> 01:54.297
Oh!

02:01.039 --> 02:02.105
David Rossi.

02:02.107 --> 02:04.591
David, I just finished
the manuscript.

02:04.593 --> 02:07.760
You are a crime novel artiste.

02:07.762 --> 02:09.262
The Butcher returns.

02:09.264 --> 02:11.381
The Piano Man sings.

02:11.383 --> 02:14.601
The Queen of Diamonds
is Lady X. Wow.

02:14.603 --> 02:17.820
The new book is absolutely
fantabulous, my friend.

02:17.822 --> 02:20.106
It's compelling, captivating...

02:20.108 --> 02:21.274
But...

02:21.276 --> 02:24.277
It's incomplete.
Where is the dedication page?

02:24.279 --> 02:25.995
I didn't think you'd notice.

02:25.997 --> 02:27.247
I'm paid to notice.

02:27.249 --> 02:28.564
Well, I haven't decided.

02:28.566 --> 02:29.782
Well, hurry, would you?

02:29.784 --> 02:31.668
We're ready to go to print.

02:31.670 --> 02:33.786
Uh... I'll get right on it.

02:33.788 --> 02:34.787
Today.

02:34.789 --> 02:36.122
By the end of the week,
Amanda.

02:36.124 --> 02:37.790
I've still got my day job.

02:37.792 --> 02:39.175
Ah, yes.

02:39.177 --> 02:41.427
Lives to save,
adventures to live.

02:41.429 --> 02:42.512
I get it!

02:42.514 --> 02:44.881
You really don't.

02:45.966 --> 02:48.635
Someone is heating things up
in Santa Monica

02:48.637 --> 02:51.588
and they are not sharing
the sunblock.

02:51.590 --> 02:54.524
3 charred bodies have shown up
at the pier in the last week.

02:54.526 --> 02:55.975
M.E. cannot identify
the victims.

02:55.977 --> 02:58.611
She can tell us
that two are male

02:58.613 --> 03:00.196
and the latest victim
is a female.

03:00.198 --> 03:01.648
Well, if he's crossing
gender lines,

03:01.650 --> 03:03.599
we can probably rule out
sexual assault.

03:03.601 --> 03:06.119
Was the coroner able to determine
the exact cause of death?

03:06.121 --> 03:07.787
No. The results
were inconclusive,

03:07.789 --> 03:10.206
but my money
is on the obvious.

03:10.208 --> 03:11.607
It might not be that simple.

03:11.609 --> 03:13.826
If the unsub's connected
to the victims,

03:13.828 --> 03:16.546
burning the bodies might be
an attempt to mask their identity.

03:16.548 --> 03:19.115
Or he's sophisticated enough
to know the fire will eliminate

03:19.117 --> 03:20.800
the evidence
of his murder rituals.

03:20.802 --> 03:22.752
This takes time.

03:22.754 --> 03:24.804
If he's burning his victims
while they're alive,

03:24.806 --> 03:26.956
it's not just sadistic.
He's patient.

03:26.958 --> 03:29.458
And organized. He'd need
access to materials

03:29.460 --> 03:30.960
necessary for burning
a human body

03:30.962 --> 03:32.628
and a space to do so
undetected.

03:32.630 --> 03:34.147
Has anyone
been reported missing?

03:34.149 --> 03:35.431
Nobody that's a match.

03:35.433 --> 03:37.400
I'm running dental records
in there right now, though.

03:37.402 --> 03:40.186
Then the problem is we're
not even sure the victims are local.

03:40.188 --> 03:41.904
That pier is a popular
photo op.

03:41.906 --> 03:43.273
He could be hunting tourists.

03:43.275 --> 03:45.308
Or warning them away.
He's dropping the bodies

03:45.310 --> 03:47.527
where they can be found
quickly.

03:47.529 --> 03:48.661
He's also accelerating
his attacks.

03:48.663 --> 03:50.380
He's gone from a 4-day
cooling off period

03:50.382 --> 03:52.248
to only two days
between kills.

03:52.250 --> 03:53.616
It's all part of his plan.

03:53.618 --> 03:56.299
We need to stop him
before he makes it one.

03:56.300 --> 04:00.300
