04:00.302 --> 04:05.302
== sync, corrected by <font color="#00ff00">elderman</font> ==

04:05.327 --> 04:25.879
♪

04:31.329 --> 04:34.081
"You never find yourself
until you face the truth."

04:34.709 --> 04:35.958
Pearl Bailey.

04:36.433 --> 04:37.965
This guy's putting bodies
on display

04:37.966 --> 04:39.883
and staging their discovery
to make an impact.

04:39.885 --> 04:41.751
Oh, he wants
to be noticed,

04:41.753 --> 04:43.136
either for his handiwork

04:43.138 --> 04:44.838
or because he lacks
recognition

04:44.840 --> 04:45.972
in his everyday life.

04:45.974 --> 04:48.308
He shows no signs of remorse
for his crimes.

04:48.310 --> 04:51.377
His message is more important
than human life.

04:51.379 --> 04:53.313
He might not even see
these people as being human.

04:53.315 --> 04:55.732
Is it just me or does this
feel territorial?

04:55.734 --> 04:57.150
I think you're right.
For some reason,

04:57.152 --> 04:59.019
the pier is very
important to him.

04:59.021 --> 05:01.187
Forget flossing those
pearlies, my B.A.-Utes,

05:01.189 --> 05:02.889
'cause thanks to two
fillings,

05:02.891 --> 05:04.824
an underage drinking charge,

05:04.826 --> 05:06.776
and a very effective
M.A.D.D. Organization,

05:06.778 --> 05:08.278
I have been able to identify
the latest victim

05:08.280 --> 05:10.614
of this person barbecuer
as Lindsay Leeman,

05:10.616 --> 05:13.566
from Edina, Minnesota.
She was only 19 years of age.

05:13.568 --> 05:15.085
Her file's on your tablets.

05:15.087 --> 05:18.788
It says here she's only been
in Santa Monica a couple months.

05:18.790 --> 05:20.273
Yeah, it doesn't look like
she had a job,

05:20.275 --> 05:21.591
'cause according
to bank records,

05:21.593 --> 05:23.460
her mom's been sending her
$250 a month.

05:23.462 --> 05:25.912
Ok, so how does she afford
an Ocean Avenue address

05:25.914 --> 05:27.297
on such little income?

05:27.299 --> 05:29.182
Was she making money
under the table?

05:29.184 --> 05:30.617
Not that she was
depositing, anyway.

05:30.619 --> 05:32.519
Cell phone records
show her texting

05:32.521 --> 05:34.437
up until 7:00 last night.

05:34.439 --> 05:35.922
This unsub's
incredibly efficient.

05:35.924 --> 05:38.257
He was able to abduct, murder,
and dispose of Lindsay's body

05:38.259 --> 05:39.559
in under 12 hours.

05:39.561 --> 05:41.194
Wait, there's something else.

05:41.196 --> 05:43.813
All her communications
are to Minnesota numbers.

05:43.815 --> 05:45.282
There's not one
from California.

05:45.284 --> 05:47.584
So she lived somewhere two months
and didn't make any friends?

05:47.586 --> 05:49.602
I thought that only
happened to me.

05:49.604 --> 05:51.488
Garcia, any luck identifying
the other victims?

05:51.490 --> 05:53.657
No. Apparently fire's
my Kryptonite.

05:53.659 --> 05:55.041
But I'll keep searching.

05:59.013 --> 06:01.548
So what's he trying to say?

06:01.550 --> 06:03.717
Get out or this
could be you?

06:03.719 --> 06:05.251
Maybe.

06:05.253 --> 06:08.171
It's a pretty public area.
He's gotta be dumping late at night.

06:08.173 --> 06:09.990
Well, he blends in
when he does.

06:09.992 --> 06:12.509
Santa Monica police increased
patrol after the second body,

06:12.511 --> 06:15.562
yet he still manages
to dump Lindsay here.

06:15.564 --> 06:19.132
This guy's getting smarter
or he's got insider knowledge.

06:19.134 --> 06:20.767
We should take a look
at first responders.

06:20.769 --> 06:23.737
You know, his rage might not
be directed at tourists.

06:23.739 --> 06:26.523
If the bodies are found and
removed prior to morning rush hour,

06:26.525 --> 06:28.706
then most of them might
not even have a chance

06:28.731 --> 06:30.411
to see his work.

06:30.412 --> 06:32.412
Then who would?

06:36.985 --> 06:37.984
Hotchner.

06:37.986 --> 06:39.452
Sir, I noticed something odd.

06:39.454 --> 06:41.671
There aren't any utilities
listed in Lindsay Leeman's name,

06:41.673 --> 06:44.541
so I ran the address, and it turns out
it is not a residence,

06:44.543 --> 06:46.109
it's a private mail center.

06:46.111 --> 06:47.444
Did her family know
where she was staying?

06:47.446 --> 06:49.462
No, the apartment number
Lindsay gave her family

06:49.464 --> 06:51.464
corresponds to the mailbox
at the center.

06:51.466 --> 06:53.600
Her mom had no idea
it wasn't a home.

06:53.602 --> 06:56.019
All right, her mother's on the way
to Los Angeles to claim the body.

06:56.021 --> 06:58.221
Yeah, she just got to LAX.
I rerouted her to you.

06:58.223 --> 06:59.839
Ok. Thanks.

07:05.863 --> 07:07.981
There isn't much left.

07:07.983 --> 07:09.399
Were you able
to determine

07:09.401 --> 07:11.034
if the victims died
of immolation?

07:11.036 --> 07:13.044
An examination of the lungs
indicates Lindsay didn't

07:13.069 --> 07:14.291
breathe in smoke.

07:15.123 --> 07:17.073
So she was dead before
being set on fire.

07:17.075 --> 07:18.625
Same as the others.

07:18.627 --> 07:20.043
So how is he killing them?

07:20.045 --> 07:22.212
I was able to isolate penetrating
lacerations to the abdomen.

07:22.214 --> 07:23.463
They were stabbed.

07:23.465 --> 07:26.532
They most likely died
of exsanguination as a result.

07:26.534 --> 07:29.219
So the burning is nothing more than
a forensic countermeasure.

07:29.221 --> 07:30.273
An effective one.

07:30.298 --> 07:31.555
Not only does it destroy
trace evidence,

07:31.556 --> 07:33.423
but it makes it difficult
to identify the bodies

07:33.425 --> 07:35.258
and determine
a common victimology.

07:35.260 --> 07:38.094
Hopefully Lindsay's mother
can fill in the gaps.

07:38.096 --> 07:41.097
Why did she lie about
where she was living?

07:41.099 --> 07:43.400
That's what we're trying
to figure out.

07:43.402 --> 07:45.268
Did Lindsay know anyone
in Los Angeles

07:45.270 --> 07:47.337
before she moved here?

07:47.339 --> 07:50.657
No, she was on her own.

07:50.659 --> 07:52.158
Alone.

07:52.160 --> 07:54.310
That's very brave.

07:54.312 --> 07:59.282
She was fearless.

07:59.284 --> 08:00.917
Her dad died
when she was young,

08:00.919 --> 08:02.952
so she learned to be
independent

08:02.954 --> 08:04.537
earlier than most.

08:04.539 --> 08:06.956
Why did she leave home?

08:07.958 --> 08:10.093
She was chasing her dream.

08:10.095 --> 08:13.596
So she was performing
locally?

08:13.598 --> 08:15.565
All the time.

08:15.567 --> 08:18.084
Anywhere
she could draw a crowd.

08:18.086 --> 08:20.386
Usually the pier.

08:20.388 --> 08:22.522
Did she mention meeting
someone new?

08:22.524 --> 08:24.724
Anyone who was
offering her work?

08:24.726 --> 08:27.444
I was sending her money
until she got settled.

08:27.446 --> 08:30.613
If she needed more...

08:32.950 --> 08:37.120
Where was my daughter
living, Agent Hotchner?

